{"tid":1830133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪所有有LIHKG PIG嘅嘢都會有人撲住去買？","createTime":"2020-01-19T10:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T16:07:52.000Z","uid":259004,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"93e040612c12f672b298993f41af3cb18c98ea9f","tid":1830133,"uid":259004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"手工嘢係有佢嘅價值亦都好難去衡量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自力更新唔係一件壞事，<br />\n喺呢場運動入面有小朋友經濟上有困難，<br />\n亦都唔係個個有家長接濟，<br />\n整小手工支撐自己生活都無可厚非，<br />\n好似「香港市民貼紙小姐」咁嘅模式相信無人會反對。<br />\n<br />\n但係好似：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HRGuFG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HRGuFG.png&h=e6a193d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hpha7sn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpha7sn.png&h=d953ae53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n認真咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扣唔扣除成本都好，<br />\n用抗爭做主題，<br />\n資源到底係咪用返喺抗爭上面？<br />\n如果唔係嘅，<br />\n同垃圾經濟日報出pepe袋或者偽黃藍店有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈唔係要人做免費義工，<br />\n但係更加唔係俾人搵水魚嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n（利申：唔係反對義賣同小朋友自力更新）<br />\n（利申2：如果圖中係小弟誤會咗嘅一定會親自幫請你哋澄清加拉埋三姑六婆幫襯）"},{"pid":"91f3592a85b39d946208e1ea49854e2d5bcbbad5","tid":1830133,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1031cab9e1195d91a7125656663e74607d38d830","tid":1830133,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"連豬驚嚇版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465db061e30b1d8ba9bfbde287361914eeae3326","tid":1830133,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"連豬鳩畫版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049cc09cd07fdcd10f4c2b0ec80440308625f0a5","tid":1830133,"uid":245793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"少女版jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77525b9786aa305f2bb5272d18e5c5cd5b703b92","tid":1830133,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6c910dac89169fca71b7d9dc799b3b02951a85","tid":1830133,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"隻連豬喺51區跑出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c346243d0b3009eb44cb4850e55fe882452077","tid":1830133,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"隻豬中左幅射<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e84deb0548b59a06c2448fa743baa0c3191315","tid":1830133,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"係，買多啲，等人哋賺多啲，有連豬買樓冇難度"},{"pid":"97e7251be99ac6d8e9ade761d365861a1d81e57e","tid":1830133,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7